          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6852430-fourtriplezed?shelf=my-fiction">my-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6852430-fourtriplezed?shelf=the-classics-or-deserve-to-be">the-classics-or-deserve-to-be</a>
