          added it


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780375757907" href="/book/show/702445.Lost_Illusions">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2827902791" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16964486173073247762">I am really surprised how much I enjoyed reading it</span>

          </span>
        </div>


